===Noun===
'''limerick'''
#A [[humorous]], often [[bawdy]] [[verse]] of five [[anapestic]] lines, with the [[rhyme]] [[scheme]] ''aabba'', and typically has a 9-9-6-6-9 [[cadence]].
: ''If a [[limerick]] one is chosin'''
: ''It'd be best if one's also boosin'''
: ''Though it's funny, I fear,''
: ''One may end up in tears,''
: ''The one has one's booze for excusin'!''

